To determine the stray capacitance of a coin cell, five coin cells (2032-type) with different thickness of PTFE (Angst + Pfister AG) were assembled, as shown in Fig. 1
                      (b). For this, PTFE disks, 16 mm in diameter, were cut using a circular cutting tool (Fischer Darex circular hollow punches). By using stacked PTFE foils of two different thicknesses, i.e. 0.5 mm and 0.8 mm, the following coin cells were assembled (see Table 1
                     ).
